DeathSteel::

The pod plummeted to the earth's surface.  The ground shook as the 
pod crashed into the side of a mountain.  The pod was embedded into 
the ground by a few yards.  Steam and smoke rose around the pod as 
the surface cooled from it's entry into the earth's atmsphere.  Soon 
the pod door opened.  A large, dark figure could be seen through the 
rising smoke.  The bot strode forth.  It was a large chrome figure 
with large dragon like wings stretching from his shoulders.  He 
scanned the area.  A forest in a temperal climate. He looked to his 
left to see a large stag elk eyeing him.  He smiled at the animal 
and looked away.  A second later, he drew his sideblaster and shot 
the animal dead.  The elk lay on the ground with a large smoldering 
hole in the center mass of the animal.  DeathSteel chuckled to 
himself.  Here would be a place to start anew.  Rebuild the Predacon 
Empire.  He smiled and scanned the area for other lifeforms.
